+------+---------------------------------+----------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
| id   | c1                              | digest                           | c2                                                     | digest_text                                           |
+------+---------------------------------+----------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|    2 | DELETE FROM t1 WHERE c1 = "whh" | A66D5C4325D82467E443039AAED826F1 | DELETE FROM t1 WHERE c1 = "whh" ORDER BY c2,c3 LIMIT 2 | DELETE FROM T1 WHERE C1 = ? ORDER BY C2 , C3 LIMIT ?  |
+------+---------------------------------+----------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
